im getting my haircut 2moro im kinda nervous cuz ever since kindergarden (is that how u spell kindergarden??)...anyways...b/c ever since my kindergarden haircut where everyone thot i was a boy so my mom had to tie a bow on me so ppl had a little hint that i was a grl ..so traumatizing...so im crossing my fingers that this haircut looks good. im also going to see batman 2nite and i mite be going swimming 2day but that all happens after my dentist appt which im about to go to. i hate the dentist! but from wut i hear the office i go to just invested in vibrating/massaging chairs for everyone while they wait so thas a plus ill have fun with that. u kno wut the most annoying thing is ...ants! around this time every year my room gets infested with ants and it bugs me like nothing else duz! cuz ill be sleeping and they will be crawling on me and ill be watching tv and they'll be crawling on me and then ill reach over to pick up the remote and guess what is crawling on it ....ants ants and more ants. ahhhh! they just need to leave me alone :( 
 
i played putt putt the other day with my mom and dad for fathers day and i won and the best part was at the end if u get a whole in 1 u get a free pass for next time and whenever i get there i always cheat and throw the ball in so i get a free pass but this time i didnt want to cheat so i actually hit the ball and it went in! so i got a free pass the noble way. it made me feel good lol
http://humpthecrunch.livejournal.com/19612.html

so0 summer is goin pretty good. so far iv worked alot and stuff. and i plan on getting tanner and tanner...hopefully it'll work :) on sunday my mom thru my grandma a surprise birthday party. she was 70 and the party actually turned out pretty well. there was a lot of old ppl that i had no idea who they were but we were related so that was weird. and then 2day im goin 2 south carolina to my cousins house to spend time with my grandpa who flew in from south america. i hate going to their house but i have 2 ..they are family. i wanna see so many ppl. i wanna see ellen and ween ..we gota get 2getber soonnnnnnn and im getting a haircut so that'll bee good
http://humpthecrunch.livejournal.com/19273.html

its summer finally! wooooo...so i can tell its gunna be a great one. its been raining alot tho so hopefully that will stop cuz i gota get super tan this summer..thas my goaL! exams were biatches but they are over thankfully. and then this past sat i took the SAT ..another biatch! but me n steph got bojangles o0o sweet sweet tea b4 the SAT so that was good. and then i layed out a little bit on saturday and im gunna lay out more 2day. i wanna go 2 the beach so bad. next sunday my mom is throwing my grandma a surprise party ...its gunna be a hot party lol but yes if u wanna do anything lemme kno so we can get 2gether!
http://humpthecrunch.livejournal.com/19010.html

so kris keeps telling me that i shuld update this so i decided 2 finally do it after almost a month lol anyways not alot has happened since my last entry. prom was fun. i think me and jenna are awsome planners even if we plan everything at the last min. lol it all worked out good. we went to mama ricattas to eat and then we went 2 prom at bank of america stadium and then we went 2 the post prom party until 4 in the morning and then justin took us home and i got home at 5ish. it was a crazi nite but lots of fun. they had really good slushees at the post prom party. that was prolly my fav part of that. and we got these really comfy pants from prom. im thinkng about putting in my 2 weeks notice at work. it just dusnt fit me anymore. i loved that job when i first started and now its just like iv never dreaded anything more than i do when ihave 2 go 2 work and they always try 2 say stuff 2 me and it just makes me mad. so im thinking about just being job free over summer and getting another job when school starts again. speaking of school...only a week and then exams left! woo! i cant wait for this yr 2 be over there was just way 2 much work. then next yr will be senior yr, crazi to think of that. last nite i got off of work early and i hung out with steph. we went to on the boarder and ordered virgin daquari's (spelling) and we got made fun of by the waiters lol and then we went and saw guess who at concord mills and we saw the tony mobile! it was so exciting. it was lots of fun tho. that is wut i miss the most, being able to just hang out with my friends on fridays and saturdays. well speaking of work i gota go 2nite from 5-10 and close so that sux .....ahhh
http://humpthecrunch.livejournal.com/18765.html

so i havent written in here in almost a month. its been pretty crazi lately. lets see iv been sick like all weekend i didnt go 2 work tho which was good. proms coming up on the 14th of may. i went 2 the orthodontist 2day for an appt and fantasia barino was there ( winner on american idol last season ) and i got 2 talk 2 her and i overheard her tell her ortho that clear braces looked good on me and i was her inspiration 2 get clear braces cuz b4 i went in there she wasnt sure that she was gunna get braces but then we talked and she saw my braces and she was getting on the clear braces b4 i left so thas kinda cool i was someone famous's inspiration 2get clear braces lol. i dont have much 2 say so ill just cut this 1 short.
http://humpthecrunch.livejournal.com/18441.html

it was easter this past sunday, it wasnt that big of a deal for my fam this year i duna. and i got to see ellen and christine this past monday it was alot of fun. i miss hanging out with them. " my cats freaking out".."i wonder y that is".."b/c u smell like fuckin cheese" hah ellen that was soo great. and then i stayd the nite at her house and then tuesday we woke up and we layd out for a bit and then i left and got home and layed out somemore and then took a shower and stuff and then i went 2 pizza hut and i ended up stayin there til like 11:30 cuz i helped them close. and then wednesday i went 2 my grandmas house and was there til about 3:30 and then i came home and got ready and then went to mikes house and hung out. and then came home and watched tv and fell asleep and 2day im supposed 2 be goin 2 the mall with vickie and caitie if they can go but i duna. its OC nite...WOO!
http://humpthecrunch.livejournal.com/18424.html

so0o so0o its spring break which is excellent. lets see tuesday i drove 2 school then me n steph got outta school at 11:15 and we went 2 qdoba's for lunch then we went home then wednesday i went shopping with my mom at eastland mall..havent been there in 4ever. then thursday i hung out with christine that was fun we havent hung out in awhile and then yesterday i just hung around the house until it was time 4 work and then i went into work. it wasnt bad last nite i had fun with brinton and neill and the rest of the crazy kids that work there. it was busy at all which was good 4 me. and towards the very end of the nite one lady told me that i was the nicest waitress shes ever had and i was like aw thx. it made my day :) and then these 4 drunk guys came in there and brinton and neill were trying 2 make me take the table and i was like o0 hell no they are guys, they are drunk, and they are saying stuff 2 me when i walk past them i dont think so and so neill ended up taking the table. and i got 2 leave work a lil early last nite and then this morning i woke up early and went and watched brinton and neill play a basketball game and then after that we all went out 2 lunch and hung out 4 a bit and then i came back home and got ready and here i am waiting to go back to work and monday im hangin out with ellen that shuld bee awsome like always and then hopefully hanging with vickie and caitie b sometime this week. shuld be fun shuld be fun

happy birthday 2 brinton! yay..

Anywho.. this week had to be the best week ever at school. we had school monday then tuesday we went 2 school but got out at 11 cuz the roof blew off lol and then wednesday we had no school and 2day there was school but my mom let me stay home and 2moro theres no school and then the weekend ..how great!

lets see...last friday i went 2 work, saturday i went 2 the mall with brinton and neill and saw be cool and went 2 work then sunday went 2 brintons 2 watch the unc and duke game with him, neill, brintons gf, and this kid james. it was aight. then monday i went 2 school then went 2 pizza hut and picked up my check and then tuesday got outta school early, then went 2 the orthdontist later and then went to work to help brinton out. and then went home found out there was no school wed...great news..then went 2 bed and then woke up and went with my mom and my gma to different places and then went and watched my gma get her hair done and then i came home and got brintons present 2gether and took it 2 his house ..tuesday nite at work he told me that he really liked the blue m&m's so i got a bag of m&m's and took out all of the blue ones and put this in this lil blue container and then i put that in a blue bag and a blue ribbon and wrote him a birthday card on blue paper and then gave it 2 him lol he seemed like he liked it so thas cool and then i went back home and then 2day i stayed home from school and went 2 the mall got a tanktop and then came back home and now im waiting 2 see when my brothers gf is coming over cuz she invitd me 2 go 2 lunch with her and some of her friends and then later my fam and i are goin 2 her soccer game at central cabarrus. and after that i have no idea. and 2moro i duna wut im doin, and then saturday are the SAT's. fun fun fun
http://humpthecrunch.livejournal.com/17486.html

my arm is all better. i went 2 the doctor 2day and they said its all good n better so thas a good thing. my weekend was pretty good. lets see friday i was supposed 2 go 2 ellens house but she got grounded so that didnt happen. i was sad. so i went 2 dinner with my family at this fish place with a big whale on the front sign its gr8 ..christine knows what restaurant im talkin about. and yeh we were paying for it and the lady that was checkin us out was like o0o my ...ur one pretty lady and i was like o0 thank u and she was like wow grl u culd be a model and i was like ha thx and then she asked my parents if i was in modeling and they were like um no..and she was like grl u shuld be 1 ur really pretty and i was like thx lol and then we left ..u dont see that everyday and then saturday i woke up got ready me and my mom went 2 the mall i was goin shoppin but ended up not buying anything dont ya hate when that happens lol and then brinton and neill met me up there around 2ish and we hung out for awhile and then they were takin me back home and then they talked me into goin into work so i got my stuff and we all went 2 work and work was actually really fun. everyone gave me hugs cuz they hadnt seen me in liek 2 weeks so it was nice i felt loved :) we ended up bein done at like 12 and neill drove me back home and then i went 2 sleep and then sunday i woke up and just kinda chilled out and then i started my history paper at 4:30 and finished around 7:15..ahh it took 4 frickin ever. its 6 pages. and then 2day i woke up went 2 target and some places with my mom and then we went 2 the doctor and then back home and i did my religion project then i went 2 the library 2 print it and then back home and i drove my car up and down my street it was so weird cuz it felt like i had no idea how 2 drive. and then i took a shower and now im here. and that was my weekend...

the penguin beside my mood is so cute..its like jumpin all around lol
http://humpthecrunch.livejournal.com/17277.html

aight well im sure by now u all kno about my arm incident but if there are any lingering thots about it ...heres wut happened i was at work last sat nite and i was taking (ranch) sald dressing back 2 the freezer and they mopped the floors and i was walked rite into it and slipped fell on my left elbow/arm woke up the next day my arm culdnt move went 2 the ER got an arm sling and im still in it. yeh public schools suck...they have 2moro and monday off from school. and of course we have school..gr8. but we have the 21st of feb off so thas in like 2 weeks. and i dont get 2 work for the next 2 weekends due to my arm issue. 3rd quarter seriously kills me every year it seems like. so many projects, and essays, and homework...they need 2 lay off a lil bit. christines getting her hair cute 2day i cant wait 2 see it 2moro! its gunna be so different but im sure it'll look cute :) 

i miss ellen........
http://humpthecrunch.livejournal.com/16956.html

this week has been crazi..dodgeball games, mass with the throat blessing, and homeroom teachers calling their homerooms jerks.i luv it. but neways last nite i went 2 work i really wanted 2 be at the concert at tremont watching sugarcult and hawthorne heights but o0o well. it was ok last nite at work. brinton made me the most beutiful rose ..he made it out of duck tape and its just so0 pretty. ill take a pic of it sumtime and show it. it was my valentines day present just a lil early. it was def the sweetest thing iv ever gotten. but he was bein kinda mean last nite i duna y. so i just didnt talk 2 him much. and then 2nite i gota go into work. its just me and neill 2nite. well i dont have much 2 update so i guess im done 4 now. :)
http://humpthecrunch.livejournal.com/16824.html

AH! its so0o cold outside. my mom let me skip school yesterday 4 no reason at all lol it was her idea and i was all up 4 it. shes the coolest mom lol. so i just hung out with her until i had 2 go 2 work last nite. it was fun. i luv working fridays. it was just me and brinton last nite. we didnt get a table until like 6:30 and we both got 2 work at 5. and then after 6:30 we had like an hr of complete madness with table after table come in and then after about 8 we had acouple more tables and then it was like 9:30 and then we had like no tables and then we had 2 clean up and stuff. it was so0 weird cuz we saw these ppl who kept coming in and out of the front door and i saw 1 of them coming towards where me and brinton were and then i realized it was steph lol ..so0o random. i also got 2 watch brinton plunge a toilet last nite fun stuff. and then i left. i have a feeling that 2nite is gunna suck cuz neill is outta town so its just gunna be me serving thas gunna suck alot. hopefully like noone will come in there 2 eat. 2nite is homecoming at catholic. i hope everyone whose going has a gr8 time. take lots of pix 4 me 2 see!

we had no school this past wednesday. it was random but good. it wulda been better if we had fri off but its ok we have monday off which is good. lets see here friday i left school a lil early and then i went home and got ready 4 work i went 2 work and had a lot of fun. me and neill and brinton are really good friends now. they r cool kids and they r both really nice. like i was really stressing out cuz there were so many ppl that came in friday for dine in and it was my turn 2 take another table and this table of 7 ppl came in and brinton was like its ur turn and i was like aight and then i figured out that i wuldnt be able to handle it and so i asked brinton if hed take the table for me and he was like i cant i have like 7 tables so i asked neill and he said the same thing and then i was like omg neill please please take it and then brinton overheard and he was like ..here get their drinks and ill take the table for u and i was like r u sure? and he was like yeh i wanna help u and i was like aw. and then he told at the end of the nite these 3 mexicans in cowboy hats came in the store and i was cleaning the dineing room and stuff and then i went 2 clean the bathrooms and brinton washelping me and he was like u kno they were checkin u out rite and i was like they were? and he was like yeh and then he was like but i culd def see y theyd check u out and i was like o0 yeh im sure this pizza hut outfit displays sexy all over and he was like nah ur beutiful and i was like aw thx. and then he was tellin neill about it and they were like its a guy thing and i was like o0o and they were like yeh i mean we've all checked u out and i was like o0o this is all new news 2 me lol and then brinton showed me his car that he has like a remote control 4 ..like u press a button and the car starts its so cool! lol and then i went home and then last nite it was so0o0o funny...this drunk lady and her husband came in and neill took them and like he looked so scared everytime he walked over to that table and the lady was like giving him high 5's and stuff and she smoked in our bathroom and yeh it was just weird but funny. and joe came back for this weekend. it was a surprise. i wasnt expecting to ever see him again but there he was when i went into work on friday. weird. and then 2day i duna wut im doin and same with 2moro i have no idea wut im doin. but i just realized that this is a long entry so im gunna stop typing. <3

so0o let me update u ...nuthin really 2 exciting i just felt the need 2 update 2nite. i got my check from work $118. its my highest so far. lets see friday nite i worked, sat nite i worked and this table of like a lot of ppl came in and it was insane iv never had so many kids run into me ...ahhh crazi hyper kids who have had way 2 much pizza dont work 2 well 4 me but on a better note ..i got 2 see ellen on sunday! ahh that was awsome. we finally got 2 have our alone time that we really needed. we got 2 catch up on some good times and laughs. we went 2 khols and then harassed patti at target haha! o0o man that was gr8. then we went 2 birkdale for like 5 min then we were leaving and got behind these 2 guys and they were like gangsta fosho. they had 1 of those my other ride is ur mom stickers on the back of their POS car if i mite add. and then they had a air freshener that said fo shizzle but me and ellen culdnt read it so we were like .."my shoe?"..."my sandal"...we were tryin 2 figure it out and then ellen saw it. and then we started racing them down the street and we so won! and then we went back 2 ellens and hung out then i left and got ready 4 skool. we dont have skool on wednesday..random..but hey its a day off cant really complain. then we have the following monday off. i decided that im not goin 2 sadie hawkins. i didnt have fun last yr or the yr b4 really and besides ill prolly have 2 work anyways so im just not gunna go but i hope that all of u that do go have a lovely time <3 and yeh i really cant wait til like spring break/ summer. i miss the summer. and if anyone wants 2 go on a beach trip or major roadtrip and wants 2 drive or find sumone 2 drive then def. let me know cuz i really wanna go sumwhere..minus the parents.. for spring break..ya kno wut im sayin?

break is over and i really dont wanna go back 2 school 2moro im def. not ready 2 go back. this break has been really fun 4 me. i thot it was gunna be boring but it wasnt that bad. tuesday i went 2 the mall with jen and then friday i went to the mall with christine and then me, chrisitne, and her mom went 2 macado's 2 eat. and then i had 2 go 2 work. i duna wut happened 2 my left foot but its killing me. its all bruised and i can barely walk on it and its bad. lol omg i ate so much food 2day maybe cuz i was bored. o0o well wut can ya do? im home alone rite now my parents went 2 some ladys party and my bro is somehwer and my sister is sumwhere. and im here. fun fun fun. well im gunna go take a bubble bath or sumthin. have a good nite and ill c most of u 2moro

ahhhh i really hate saying goodbye 2 people. it makes me so sad. i went into work yesterday around 12 and joe was there. and it was basically me, joe, jessica, and tiffany working so that was cool. joe was nicer than ever yesterday which only made it 10 times harder to say goodbye. i was supposed 2 leave at 5 but i stayed 2 help cuz it got really busy then i was suppose 2 leave at 8 but i got a table at the last min so i stayed and then i just ended up stayin til like 9:45. and i clocked out got my stuff went over 2 joe gave him a hug told him good luck and he was all like thers been some good times here and i was like yeh and then we just said bye and then i left. it was sad. maybe he'll visit. i gota go pick up my check sumtime 2day. well im watching never been kissed on tv so im gunna go back 2 watching that and i hope everyone had a good christmas!

wednesday: i got my after 9 license. went 2 play putt putt with steph then went 2 birkdale for awhile then went 2 pizza hut and then went 2 see meet the fockers. it was gr8 not having 2 be home at 9
....thursday i did nuthing....
friday: went into work at 3. joe told me that this coming monday is gunna be his last day at our pizza hut then after monday hes goin on sumwhere else. at first i thot he was just kiddin but then after awhile i figured out he was bein serious. it made me sad 2 hear that cuz hes my fav. manager. at first i didnt like him at all and i thot he was a jerk and just lately we started 2 be buddy buddy and nice 2 eachother and now hes leaving. im gunna miss him. 2moro im working so hopefully he'll bee there so i can say goodbye and stuff. ah i hate the saying goodbye part. brandon walked me 2 my car last nite when i left work cuz it was really dark and i was parked on the other side of the parking lot and he didnt want me 2 walk alone so he walked with me i thot that was nice.then i came home and we opened presents
